                <publisher>Printed by <hi rend="italic">M. F. </hi>for [J]OHN MARRIOT,<lb/>and are to be sold at his shop in St <hi rend="italic">Dunstans</hi><lb/>Church-yard in <hi rend="italic">Fleet-street. </hi></publisher><docDate>1633.</docDate></docImprint>
            
            
